    "en": {
      "title": "President Ranil is going to China",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan Ambassador to China has said that he plans to visit China to discuss cooperation in trade, investment and tourism.",
        "He told an international media that Sri Lanka has requested China to help in trade, investment and tourism.",
        "In Colombo. Kohana said Beijing could help Sri Lanka by investing more in China-backed mega port projects in Ambandottai as well.",
        "He also said that he expects no fundamental change in the policy of the new government regarding China. (a)"
      ],
